  dialogueLibrary:
  - id: intro_1
    entries:
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: The story you will hear today, happened a long time ago.
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: The story of two women, who loved each other more than life.
  - id: intro_2
    entries:
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: "The first of them, Isobel\u2014powerful, ruthless, living in her cold,
        lonely castle away from others. "
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: Despite her wealth and the legion of servants there was no one that could
        bring her the warmth of human touch, she craved so immensely.
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: That was until Bella came into her life.
  - id: intro_3
    entries:
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: Bella was kind, warm and gentle, bringing Isobel everything the castle
        was missing.
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: It didn't take long for Bella's warmth to melt Isobel's long-frozen heart.
  - id: intro_4
    entries:
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: They lived happily for a long time, away from people and in peace.
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: They didn't yet know that their peace would soon be disturbed by an unwelcome
        guest.
  - id: intro_5
    entries:
    - speaker: ???
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: Foul beast! Come out and face me, so that I can end your wretched existence!
    - speaker: ???
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: I have found your lair at last, and came here to free this poor, innocent
        girl!
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: What nonsense you utter, she is happy here. Happier than she ever was
        amongst your kind.
    - speaker: ???
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: Lies! No one could be happy with a monster like you!
    - speaker: ???
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: I, Sonnet, the greatest mage in the land, will make sure this fair maiden
        is rescued from your claws.
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: A beautiful girl like her deserves to be much more than just a blood
        supply for a monster.
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: What?! You would dare-! Bella, stay back, let me rid us of this pest.
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: Isa... be careful...
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: Worry not, my love, I promise, I will hurry back into your arms.
  - id: intro_6
    entries:
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: But hurry back she did not. The mage's attack brought her down, and before
        she knew, her body was broken, her soul starting to slip away.
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: ISOBEL!
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: Be calm, dear maiden, the foul beast is no more.
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: No...! No... please, no...
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: What? You would weep after that monster?
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: You must be enthralled, nothing else could explain this.
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: I must lock you here, for your own safety, until the creature's spell
        wears off.
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: "That very same \u201Ccreature\u201D was struggling to hold on, the last
        sparks of her undead life being extinguished."
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: The last thing she saw before dying was her beloved, being dragged away
        from her corpse, crying out for her.
  - id: intro_7
    entries:
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: The next thing she saw was red walls and flowing magma, as she woke up
        in Hell.
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: Even though her body fell, her soul persevered, holding on, dragging
        her to the fiery pits.
  - id: tutorial_1
    entries:
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: Argh! That fucking mage!
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: "I need to get out of here. I can\u2019t let this \u201CSonnet\u201D
        harm my Bella."
  - id: tutorial_2
    entries:
    - speaker: Succubus
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 09607f1ffa6381e498030ddc7f03ba9b, type: 3}
      text: "Well, well, hello there, pretty. My name is Vellaia, who might you be?\r"
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: "Can you tell me how I can leave this accursed place?\r\r"
    - speaker: Vellaia
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 09607f1ffa6381e498030ddc7f03ba9b, type: 3}
      text: "Why in such a rush, darling? Stay for a bit, relax, have some fun.\r\r\r"
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: "I have no time for your foolishness, fiend. I need to leave.\r\r\r"
    - speaker: Vellaia
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 09607f1ffa6381e498030ddc7f03ba9b, type: 3}
      text: "This is paradise. No duties, nothing but pleasure\u2026 and sometimes
        pain. Why would you want to leave? You got someone waiting for you?\r\r\r"
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: "Yes. I have to get back to my beloved.\r\r\r"
    - speaker: Vellaia
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 09607f1ffa6381e498030ddc7f03ba9b, type: 3}
      text: "How boring. I was hoping you\u2019d stay here for a while with me. But
        I have bad news for you, sweetheart. You\u2019re not leaving this place,
        until there is a soul back in your body.\r\r\r"
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: A soul? Any soul you say?
  - id: tutorial_3
    entries:
    - speaker: Succubus
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 09607f1ffa6381e498030ddc7f03ba9b, type: 3}
      text: "Hm? Where did you come from? \r"
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: "Where did you come from? Why are you in my castle?\r\r"
    - speaker: Succubus
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 09607f1ffa6381e498030ddc7f03ba9b, type: 3}
      text: "We were summoned to protect the castle and the girl, Bella, the mage\u2019s
        paramour.\r\r\r"
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: "The mage\u2019s WHAT?!\r\r"
  - id: tutorial_4
    entries:
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: "This cannot be. I have to save my Bella. I will save her, no matter
        how many times I have to crawl out of Hell.\r\r\r"
  - id: main_1
    entries:
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: "What the-? That fucking\u2026 casting some spell, changing all the corridors
        in my castle. No matter. I\u2019ll always find my way to my Bella. Nothing
        will stop me.\r\r\r"
  - id: boss_1
    entries:
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: "I can\u2019t believe she\u2019s gone... my Isa..."
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: Quit your sobbing, my dear. Soon the spell will fade, and you will see
        that your so-called lover was nothing but a bloodsucking monster.
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: The only monster here is you.
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: "We\u2019ll work on that attitude."
  - id: boss_2
    entries:
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: You'll do no such thing, scum.
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: Isa...!
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: What?! How?! I killed you!
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: Clearly not well enough.
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: "Ugh! Doesn\u2019t matter. I\u2019ll do it again."
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: "And this time you\u2019re not coming back."
  - id: boss_3
    entries:
    - speaker: Sonnet
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: af5ca1375eda175488ddfb7bc39519cd, type: 3}
      text: NO! I will not be defeated by a lowly monster.
  - id: final_1
    entries:
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: Isa!
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: You...
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: I...
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: I was sure I lost you.
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: I promised you I would be back, didn't I?
  - id: final_2
    entries:
    - speaker: Bella
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d335b890e318bee44aae2f2616ef1db0, type: 3}
      text: Never scare me like that again.
    - speaker: Isobel
      portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d399970142ec43649bff3c67c0951c0d, type: 3}
      text: I will do my best.
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: And that is how this story ends.
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: The Lovers reunited.
  - id: final_3
    entries:
    - speaker: 
      portrait: {fileID: 0}
      text: The Magician defeated.
  - id: final_4
    entries: []
  - id: final_5
    entries: []
